text: And when Aaron and his sons have wrapped up the sanctuary in the vessels thereof, at the removing of the camp, then shall the sons of Cath enter in to carry the things wrapped up, and they shall not touch the vessels of the sanctuary, lest they die. These are the burdens of the sons of Cath in the Tabernacle of the Covenant.
